      "layout": "The layout follows a max-width contained page model for most content, with a centered alignment. The hero section is full-bleed, using a 'Deep Forest' (#1d0b0d) background with food photography and centered text (`Limón`, `See our menu`) often in 'Marigold Zest' (#f7ea48) or 'Pure White' (#ffffff). Section rhythm alternates between full-bleed imagery and content blocks with 'Vanilla Cream' (#fcf9f0) backgrounds. Content is organized into a flexible grid pattern, often featuring 3-column product cards with images above descriptive text and 'Order Now' ghost buttons. Vertical spacing is comfortable, with a '30px' section gap observed. The navigation is a fixed top bar with minimalist links.",
